      • newHandler

        public jetbrains.mps.messages.IMessageHandler newHandler​(@NotNull
                                                         String name,
                                                         boolean clear)
        Parameters:
        name - identifies named collection of messages, value is visible in UI as the name of the collection.
        clear - true if caller doesn't need to keep messages already reported under same named handler (if any)
        Returns:
        handler that pipes messages to designated UI component, never null

      • getMessageList

        @NotNull
public jetbrains.mps.messages.IMessageList getMessageList​(@NotNull
                                                          String name,
                                                          MessageListOptions... options)
        Creates/retrieves existing named collection of messages, with respect to supplied options.
        Parameters:
        name - name of the list. It's up to caller to provide reasonable name in case of MessageListOptions.AlwaysNew to tell one list from another.
        options - if no options specified, MessageListOptions.ReuseExisting + MessageListOptions.ActivateOnMessage is assumed.
        Returns:
        UI-backed collection of messages.
